  "texts": [
    "LSTM has been employed for HSI spectral classification by Mou et al. (2017).",
    "Corresponding to a sample pixel vector, each band forms a sequential input to the LSTM model.",
    "To fuse spatial information into the spectral classification, Liu et al. (2018) proposed multilayer LSTM for spatial-spectral feature extraction.",
    "Pan et al. (2020) offered single gate recurrent unit GRU for combined spectral-spatial feature extraction in the HSI classification task.",
    "A combination of 1D convolution operation and RNN have been used by Wu and Prasad (2017), primarily for extracting spectral feature vectors, the 1D convolution operation is employed and then the spectral feature sequences are fed to RNN along with the support of fully connected layers and SoftMax function to achieve HSI classification."
